, 9%; >9%), and either to MET or AVM.

 At randomization, Visit 3 (Week 0), subjects were initiated at Dose Level 1.

 Treatment with AVM was initiated at a dose of 4 mg/500 mg and titrated up to a maximum total daily dose of AVM 8 mg/2000 mg.

 Treatment with MET therapy was initiated at a dose of 500 mg and titrated up to a maximum daily dose of 2000mg.

