This study will evaluate the longer-term glycemic effect of two medicines approved for initial treatment of type 2 diabetes.

 The study consists of a 2 week screening period (2 study visits), followed by an 80 week double-blind treatment period (11 study visits).

 Also, a sub-study was included to look at changes in bone mineral density (BMD) at the lumbar spine.

